      "description": "Three mesh densities (coarse 2.1 M, medium 5.4 M, fine 11.8 M cells) were evaluated for the nominal operating point. The normalised haemolysis index changed by less than 2 % between the medium and fine meshes, confirming adequate spatial resolution for the quantity of interest.",
