      "rationale": "The bench data-collection study recorded fluid temperature (37 ± 0.5 °C), haematocrit (33 ± 1 %), and heparin concentration for each operating point. All parameters fell within the ranges specified in the test plan. Condition documentation is considered adequate for a level-2 assessment."
