      "rationale": "The relative haemolysis index (RH) is derived from the modified power-law model of Giersiepen et al. and is directly proportional to plasma-free haemoglobin release, the clinically relevant endpoint. The mapping between the computational QoI and the clinical endpoint is documented in the modelling assumptions report."
